Package: LaurentDetect
Type: Package
Title: Detect Financial Singularities Using Laurent Series
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Etienne", "Abate", email = "abateetienne18@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements Laurent series approximation to detect singularities, 
    shocks, and anomalies in financial time series. The package provides tools 
    for loading financial data, computing local Laurent approximations, detecting 
    singularities based on the principal part norm, and visualizing results. 
    Designed for quantitative finance applications in risk management and market analysis.
